<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Delhi//PadelCollective — Hub</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;0,900;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { background: #f5f3ef; color: #111; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; min-height: 100vh; }

  header {
    background: #000; color: #fff;
    padding: 0 40px; height: 60px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
  }
  .logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; }
  .logo .sl { color: #444; font-weight: 400; }
  .pip-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #555; }
  .pip { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: #4ade80; border-radius: 50%; animation: pip 2s infinite; }
  @keyframes pip { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:.3} }

  /* HERO */
  .hero { background: #000; color: #fff; padding: 56px 40px 48px; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #444; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .hero h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 58px); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.0; letter-spacing: -2px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: #666; }
  .hero p { color: #555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; max-width: 420px; }

  /* CARDS */
  .cards-wrap {
    max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 40px 80px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px;
  }

  .card {
    background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e0ddd7;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden; text-decoration: none; color: #111;
    transition: box-shadow .2s, transform .2s;
  }
  .card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.14); transform: translateY(-4px); }

  .card-top { background: #000; color: #fff; padding: 32px 30px 28px; flex: 1; }
  .card-icon { font-size: 30px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .card-label { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #555; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .card-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .card-desc { font-size: 13px; color: #666; line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 300; }

  .card-footer {
    background: #000; border-top: 1px solid #1c1c1c;
    padding: 18px 30px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .card-footer span { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #fff; }
  .arrow { font-size: 18px; color: #fff; transition: transform .2s; }
  .card:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(5px); }

  /* Ranking card slightly different shade */
  .card.ranking .card-top { background: #0f0f0f; }
  .card.ranking .card-footer { background: #0f0f0f; border-top-color: #222; }

  footer { background: #000; color: #333; text-align: center; padding: 22px; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    header, .hero { padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 38px; }
    .cards-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 28px 20px 60px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo">Delhi<span class="sl">//</span>PadelCollective</div>
  <div class="pip-wrap"><span class="pip"></span>Members Hub</div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">Welcome</div>
  <h1>Your padel<br/><em>hub.</em></h1>
  <p>Everything Delhi//PadelCollective in one place. Book a session or check where you stand.</p>
</section>

<div class="cards-wrap">

  <a class="card" href="https://dpc-padel.github.io/Calender/">
    <div class="card-top">
      <div class="card-icon">📅</div>
      <div class="card-label">Sessions</div>
      <div class="card-title">Event Calendar</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Browse upcoming sessions, check open slots, join the waitlist, and mark your interest — all in one place.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-footer">
      <span>Open Calendar</span>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </div>
  </a>

  <a class="card ranking" href="https://dpc-padel.github.io/Ranking/">
    <div class="card-top">
      <div class="card-icon">🏆</div>
      <div class="card-label">Standings</div>
      <div class="card-title">Player Rankings</div>
      <div class="card-desc">See where you stand in the collective. Live rankings updated after every session played.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-footer">
      <span>View Rankings</span>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </div>
  </a>

</div>

<footer>Delhi<span style="color:#1a1a1a">//</span>PadelCollective &mdash; Wanna play padel? Start here.</footer>

</body>
</html>
